{"tid":1327500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"迪卡儂物資採購","createTime":"2019-07-17T15:23:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T15:45:29.000Z","uid":261842,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b7ec3346eb1bdae612a8e8789c29e8ef66c5e599","tid":1327500,"uid":261842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T15:23:23.000Z","msg":"好多間Decathlon都無貨點算？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69a10fc3fcc5963f3164eae99bb4d3e29d7cd250","tid":1327500,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T15:25:20.000Z","msg":"求其memo 紙就得啦"},{"pid":"2c2f2d442a6d77d6e3eccfb2b1a6a801ff42f35b","tid":1327500,"uid":35842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T15:27:23.000Z","msg":"[721見] 如何正確隱藏身份 (整合+進階篇)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1327279\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1327279</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=9Pobuw7Wk2k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9Pobuw7Wk2k&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQsiq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=e1790da0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=9Pobuw7Wk2k</a> <br />\n唔想專登買面罩其實用Tee都得<br />\n<br />\n✅ DNS用1.1.1.1（尤其係3HK、HKT用戶）<br />\n✅ 上討論區用Tor Browser，但唔好用Tor Browser Login 任何帳號<br />\n✅ P2P通訊用Telegram / Signal<br />\n✅ Group通訊用Signal<br />\n✅ 即時戰略遊戲用Playstation Message傾<br />\n✅ 電話唔好用指紋/面容解鎖<br />\n✅ 重要嘢面談<br />\n✅ 食煙嘅你買個打火機同包純薄萬傍身<br />\n✅ 飲酒嘅你飲樽裝好飲過罐裝<br />\n✅ 有時毒撚一個更開心，唔洗吓吓同人一齊玩<br />\n✅ 毒撚自己一個玩，唔好去多狗地方玩<br />\n<br />\n❌ 咪撚帶八達通同信用卡<br />\n❌ 咪撚著拖鞋短褲同容易辨認嘅衣物<br />\n❌ 咪撚咁傻仔帶啲唔合理嘅物品係身，例如拍戲道具<br />\n❌ 咪撚除/拉低口罩<br />\n❌ 咪撚影人樣，影狗同影景就夠<br />\n<br />\n❗關閉電話上所有Facebook、WhatsApp同Instagram權限<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1629975780370609/posts/2528022960565882?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1629975780370609%2Fposts%2F2528022960565882%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQsiq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=167010bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1629975780370609/posts/2528022960565882?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://github.com/cybersec-hk/digital_awareness_hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fcybersec-hk%2Fdigital_awareness_hk&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQsiq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=3ba1d99a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">github.com/cybersec-hk/digital_awareness_hk</a>"},{"pid":"168b75768f36f6816a62582ca58b17460bbb0f46","tid":1327500,"uid":214502,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T15:30:39.000Z","msg":"咪有間Online買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16a648a196bd95aa7a087f6a7d823fba358e8de2","tid":1327500,"uid":19217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T15:34:37.000Z","msg":"Web買 幾日送到"},{"pid":"652e80e733c639fe4764e13364966e99322d26e1","tid":1327500,"uid":20820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T15:35:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ebf02a77031261bce89224601fc23bdd2de9643","tid":1327500,"uid":59618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T15:45:29.000Z","msg":"睇你買乜，後備去ssp 特賣場睇睇"}]}